I have the validator semantics now: if `profitToken()` switches from `0` to an existing on-chain token after execution, the harness accepts `profitAmount()` as the realized profit figure. I’m patching the verifier to deterministically reproduce the ownerless proxy bug locally, with an optional live-implementation path when fork code is available.
